snippet.title: Newer Super Mario Bros. Wii - RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Newer Super Mario Bros. Wii is a fan game hack project, with tons of new features, including new maps, worlds, enemies, powerups, music and more.

The game can be downloaded for free at http://www.newerteam.com

The installation process is also described there, and requires no piracy or permanent modifications to be done to your Wii console.
